## Execution Steps

1.  **Backup**: Ensure `llxprt-code-4` is clean.
2.  **Port Files**: Write the content of source files to target files.
3.  **Merge Layouts**: Apply smart edits to target [DefaultAppLayout.tsx](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/llxprt-code/packages/cli/src/ui/layouts/DefaultAppLayout.tsx) and [AppContainer.tsx](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/llxprt-code/packages/cli/src/ui/AppContainer.tsx) to integrate the components.
4.  **Verification**:
    - Run `npm install` in target (if needed).
    - Run `npm run lint` & `npm run typecheck` in target.
    - Run the new test harness `node scripts/oldui-tmux-harness.js`.

